---
import SiteLayout from "../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";

const jsonLd = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Organization",
  name: "PoE2 Hub",
  url: "https://poe2hub.net",
  contactPoint: {
    "@type": "ContactPoint",
    email: "contact@poe2hub.net",
    contactType: "customer support"
  }
};
---
<SiteLayout
  title="About PoE2 Hub"
  description="PoE2 Hub is an independent guide site for Path of Exile 2, covering build guides, boss fight breakdowns, league mechanics, and free tools like the Build Planner and Chromatic Orb Calculator."
>
  <h1>About PoE2 Hub</h1>

  <h2>What is PoE2 Hub</h2>
  <p>
    PoE2 Hub is an independent guide and reference site for Path of Exile 2,
    built by players, for players. Every page aims to answer a real question a
    player actually has, with working detail rather than filler. We put together
    build guides, boss fight breakdowns, league mechanic explainers, and practical
    tools, cross-checked against official sources and established community guides
    rather than assembled from guesswork.
  </p>

  <h2>Our standards</h2>
  <p>
    Game data on this site is cross-checked against multiple independent
    sources, including the game files themselves where possible. Where a
    value could not be confirmed, we say so instead of presenting it as
    fact. Pages that depend on patch-specific numbers state which game
    version they apply to.
  </p>

  <h2>Our Tools</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong><a href="/build-planner/">Build Planner</a></strong> — pick your class and Ascendancy, get an instant gear, gem, and passive tree recommendation.</li>
    <li><strong><a href="/chromatic-calculator/">Chromatic Orb Calculator</a></strong> — exact probability and expected orb cost for any socket color combination.</li>
    <li><strong><a href="/loot-filter-generator/">Loot Filter Generator</a></strong> — answer a few questions, get a working .filter file, no syntax knowledge required.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Content Coverage</h2>
  <p>
    As of the current patch, PoE2 Hub covers 13 boss fight guides, 22 build guides across every
    live Ascendancy, and 10 in-depth league mechanic breakdowns, alongside a class guide, trade
    guide, unique item reference, and skill gem reference. Content is updated to track current
    patches, each page carries a version note showing what it was last checked against.
  </p>

  <h2>Independence</h2>
  <p>
    PoE2 Hub is a fan-made resource. It is not affiliated with,
    sponsored by, or endorsed by Grinding Gear Games. Path of Exile 2 is a
    registered trademark of Grinding Gear Games. All game content, item names,
    and artwork referenced on this site remain the property of their
    respective owners.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions, corrections, or feedback: <a href="mailto:contact@poe2hub.net">contact@poe2hub.net</a>
  </p>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(jsonLd)} />
</SiteLayout>

<style>
  h2 { margin-top: var(--space-3); }
  ul { color: var(--text-dim); padding-left: 1.2em; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5em; }
  p { color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.75; }
</style>
